<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
	<title><%= title %></title>

	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/libs/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css" />
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/libs/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap-theme.css" />
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/style-signin.css" />

</head>
<body>
	
	<div class="login">
		<form action="/signin" method="post" class="form-horizontal">
				<div class="form-group">
					<label for="username" class="col-sm-4">Username:</label>
					
					<div class="col-sm-8">
						<input type="text" name="username" placeholder="Username" />
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="form-group">
					<label for="password" class="col-sm-4">Password:</label>
				
					<div class="col-sm-8">
						<input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" />
					</div>
				</div>	

				<div class="form-group">
					<div class="col-sm-4"></div>
					<div class="col-sm-8">
						<input type="submit" name="submit" class="btn btn-primary" />
					</div>	
				</div>
			</form>
	</div>

	<div class="banner">
		<div class="jumbotron text-center">
			<h1>Welcome to Green Bit!</h1>
			<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, quas populo complectitur ne nam, et vix deleniti reprehendunt. Alii labores delicatissimi pro ne, enim erant nominavi id nam, inimicus consequat percipitur at qui.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	
	<script type="text/javascript" src="/libs/jquery/jquery.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="/libs/jquery-backstretch/jquery.backstretch.js"></script>

	<script type="text/javascript">
		$.backstretch("/images/loginScreen.jpg");
	</script>	

</body>

</html>